title: Lassie-The Timmy Years-Selected Episodes-S05-S08  DivX
description:
Lassie-The Timmy Years
Selected Episodes-S05-S08

Only a few Lassie shows seem to have been released to the public, and mostly in collections or as single episodes on VHS.  These shows are from The Timmy Years 1958-1964 (my favorite!).  I was able to find 18 shows in various dvd collections, plus a few Christmas shows.  Here are the first 9 shows, plus the booklet that came with the Lassie 50th Anniversary Collection.

E149 The Rocking Chair
E177 The Camera
E178 Peace Patrol
E182 The Refrigerator
E199 Space Invader
E217 Wrong Gift
E254 Lassie At The Grand Canyon
E268 Wild Baby
E270 Lassie's Protege

Approx. all shows -
